{"tid":2098743,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉騙少女8萬　革職警控三罪提堂","createTime":"2020-07-07T17:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T18:56:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac0fb462f69804db6e2320088a8ed0dde44dd75","tid":2098743,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T17:04:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200707/K74PUBNPW7O4257ED4HYAQIZAY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2FK74PUBNPW7O4257ED4HYAQIZAY%2F&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=69e77c65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2FK74PUBNPW7O4257ED4HYAQIZAY%2F&h=f370a13d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200707/K74PUBNPW7O4257ED4HYAQIZAY/</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前警務人員因去年2月涉及詐騙案後，放棄職務「失更」潛逃被警方通緝，今年5月正式被革職。惟他繼續犯案，包括涉訛稱協助誤墮求職陷阱的少女追回22萬元失款，竟千上千再騙去8萬元。他被控一項詐騙罪、一項以欺騙手段取得財產罪，以及一項向16歲以下兒童作出猥褻行為罪，案件本月四日已在屯門裁判法院提堂。"},{"pid":"40e69723b3fdbc0b03478c5690ab5b10e0b0129b","tid":2098743,"uid":241504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"16歲以下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221ca978b3b10eb226be88e848393e89acff6c84","tid":2098743,"uid":273703,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"香港警察，知法犯法"},{"pid":"e25ff2faec8854d95562c85d8534b7432afc6072","tid":2098743,"uid":189417,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T17:06:39.000Z","msg":"- 咁蠢俾人呃完又呃<br />\n唔呃你呃邊個呀<br />\n<br />\n節錄LIHKG 各大苦主被騙後開嘅Post <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d40f19699551077bb996f89840324e8857cb2db","tid":2098743,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T17:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgm